The ReadAuger-Tool allows to read Auger mc-files containing monitoring and calibration data and raw-data files containing calibration histograms and FADC traces.

<---------- Prerequisits ---------->

- Externals: Available from the Auger web pages using ape.

- CDAS: The version included in the externals does not support the UUB. Since the upgrade to the UUB a new preliminary version of CDAS provided by Xavier is necessary. It can be downloaded from http://labdpr.cab.cnea.gov.ar/auger/cdas-uub.php

- boost

<---------- Installation ---------->

type 'make'
